author: A_Brickset_user
title: I am back!!! My first review of this year, i think...
review: great set and i must agree with all of the other reviews, this set is great considering you get the nesquik rabbit and it is a great to go along with the theme Racers. This set is not very old school but.....i think this set really deserves this 10/10

author: hustla187
title: Wabbit Wacing
review: This is a clever promo by Nesquick. I notice that it says that he is a cereal mascot, but he is actually not in the USA. He might be in Germany, but not out here in the US. The head is pretty cool and very rare. However, I would like to see a minifig instead of a minifig head.
